title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 14 2022
description:
Clay quickly back to 100% after Omicron. The Bidas Touch: Everything Joe Biden touches turns to crap. Another Biden adviser admits cloth masks don't work. Roberts, Kavanaugh side with libs on vaccine mandate for health care workers. C&B take calls. Should Clay wear a "This Mask Doesn't Work" mask on his next plane ride? Or, as Clay asked, is it coming to this: "Are we going to have to wear gas masks around? Is this where we're going?" Buck quizzes Clay ("Mr. Omicron Warrior") why "nature's vaccine" like his still is virtually never talked about by the "experts."
